tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE test_results (
    test_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    strategy_id INT,
    test_date TIMESTAMP,
    successful_conversions INT,
    total_visits INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (strategy_id) REFERENCES marketing_strategies(strategy_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Strategy1 (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(255),
    description TEXT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);
